data.description: Fabulous Ranch floor plan.  Open Great Room, dining Room and Kitchen! Laminate hardwood floors throughout main open area.  Kitchen has tons of cabinets , granite, breakfast bar and eating area. Huge pantry/laundry room. The enormous master suite features a huge walk in closet and romantic bath, garden tub, 4 foot ceramic tile shower and lots of counter space.  Two large secondary bedrooms separated by the living area. Upstairs is an open loft area, huge 4th bedroom and full bath. Deep two car garage w/ plenty storage space. Sit out and enjoy the fall evening on the covered front porch OR the covered rear patio.  Just off 92 before Douglas county! Fabulous level yard. Seller to Pay $4000 buyer closing costs with reasonable offer.
